cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS

The paper deals with deep neural networks and their compression, which are topics commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper specifically focuses on weight pruning, which is a technique used in machine learning and computer vision to reduce the size of deep neural networks. Therefore, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.DS.
